    6 exprs: ε
    7      | expr
    8      | expr SPACE exprs

    9 expr: CMD arith_expr
   10     | assignment
   11     | SPECIAL_CMD
   12     | CUSTOM_VAR SPACE arith_expr
   13     | COMMENT

   14 assignment: VAR SET arith_expr
